title: Google hangout with Kunal Kemmu
text:
Kunal Kemmu started off his film career as a child artist and as a lead, he made his debut with Vishesh Films' Kalyug.
After that there was no looking back for the Hum Hai Rahi Pyar Ke kid. His latest venture, Guddu Ki Gun , is an adult comedy and the actor is sure to tickle the funny bones with his performance just like he had in Golmaal 3 and Go Goa Gone .
The Times Of India has organised a Google Hangout with Kunal Kemmu on October 13 at 3 pm.
Watch this space for more.
